data %>%
  mutate(phu = case_when(phu %in% 1:10 ~ 1,
                        phu %in% 11:20 ~ 2,
                        phu %in% 21:30 ~ 3,
                        phu %in% 31:40 ~ 4,
                        phu %in% 41:50 ~ 5,
                        phu %in% 51:70 ~ 6,
                        TRUE ~ NA_real_)) %>%
  filter(is.na(phu))
